\color blue
解：
\size small
\color inherit
以球心为坐标原点建立球坐标系，令外电场为
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf{E}=E_{0}\sbf{e}_{z}$
\end_inset

，若球与地电势差为
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi_{0}$
\end_inset

，全部定解条件为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \nabla^{2}\varphi=0,\quad\left(R>R_{0}\right)\\
 & R\to\infty,\quad\varphi\to-E_{0}R\cos\theta+\varphi_{0},\quad\text{考虑势能常数}\\
 & R=R_{0},\quad\varphi=\Phi_{0}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

考虑渐进行为及边界条件，将拉普拉斯方程的通解写成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi=\varphi_{0}-E_{0}R\cos\theta+\frac{b_{0}}{R}+\frac{b_{1}}{R^{2}}\cos\theta
\]

\end_inset

代入边界条件：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi_{0}-E_{0}R_{0}\cos\theta+\frac{b_{0}}{R_{0}}+\frac{b_{1}}{R_{0}^{2}}\cos\theta=\Phi_{0}
\]

\end_inset

按
\begin_inset Formula $P_{n}\left(\cos\theta\right)$
\end_inset

的系数列方程组解得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
b_{0}=\left(\Phi_{0}-\varphi_{0}\right)R_{0},\quad b_{1}=E_{0}R_{0}^{3}
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi=\varphi_{0}-E_{0}R\cos\theta+\frac{\left(\Phi_{0}-\varphi_{0}\right)R_{0}}{R}+\frac{E_{0}R_{0}^{3}}{R^{2}}\cos\theta
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

