\begin_inset Formula $\sbf E_{0}=E_{0}\sbf e_{z}$
\end_inset

，定解条件为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \nabla^{2}\varphi_{1}=-\rho_{f}/\varepsilon,\quad R<R_{1}\\
 & \nabla^{2}\varphi_{2}=0,\quad R>R_{2}\\
 & R=0,\quad\varphi_{1}\text{有限；}R\to\infty,\quad\varphi_{2}\to-E_{0}R\cos\theta\\
 & R=R_{0}:\quad\varphi_{1}=\varphi_{2},\quad\varepsilon\frac{\partial\varphi_{1}}{\partial R}=\varepsilon_{0}\frac{\partial\varphi_{2}}{\partial R}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

因为介质球内
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{f}$
\end_inset

